The Super Eagles of Nigeria have been drawn in 2019 AFCON group B alongside Guinea and debutants Burundi and Madagascar. Nigeria is the favorite to top this group after previously winning the tournament 3 times out of the 17 times she has participated. Only Guinea can boast of some record, but nothing compared to Nigeria. While Guinea is ranked 64th in the world, Nigeria is 42. The other teams Burundi and Madagascar are only making their first appearances in the tournament. See team details including March dates and times below: